com.interpss.dstab.dynLoad

Interface DynLoadModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseDynLoadModel, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, DynamicBusDevice, DynamicDevice, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IDynamicSimulation, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DynLoadModelImpl

    public interface DynLoadModel
extends BaseDynLoadModel
    A representation of the model object 'Dyn Load Model'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Accumulated Load Change Factor
    • Load Percent
    • Load Factor
    • Load PQ
    • Init Load PQ
    • Equiv Y
    • Compensate Shunt Y
    • Curr Inj2 Net
    • Norton Cur Inj
    See Also:
    DStabDynamicLoadPackage.getDynLoadModel()
